name: Protectors of the Realm
description: WeR1 is a decentralized community whose focus is protecting and building alongside our allies in the new memecosystem Empire. The WeR1 movement encourages a positive community vibe via education of new and experienced traders in the attempt to rid the defi community of misleading members and influencers alike. WeR1 developers have created a one of kind contract with intent to strengthen our ecosystem.
